A crocodile at Lake Abaya in Ethiopia allegedly attacked and
ate a pastor on Sunday. The pastor was busy  baptising at least 80 members of his
congregation, It's reported that Pastor Docho Eshete baptised one person
and after that a crocodile jumped out of the lake and grabbed the pastor. The members of the church had to watch helplessly, as they
couldn't do anything. According to borkena.com, Lake Abaya which covers an area of
1,162 km² is known to have a huge Crocodile population.